            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1527.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>creamed coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>in 200 ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300 ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[400 ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>then add your<strong> fish sauce</strong> and <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – this is your<strong> spicy coconut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1527.-step-4-x200.jpg",
