            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop your<strong> red onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick, with a matching lid), with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp] </span><strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>onion wedges</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
