    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> spicy coconut stock</strong> and cook for a further 2-3 min or until the sauce has thickened – this is your<strong> Indonesian-style king prawn curry</strong></p><p>Fluff the<strong> basmati rice </strong>and mix with the<strong> green beans</strong> – this is your<strong> green bean rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
