    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Indonesian-style king prawn curry</strong> with the <strong>green bean rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
